          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>
            Nestled among rolling hills and sunlit trees, Pine Ridge Winery was
            founded with a simple belief: great wine begins with great moments.
          </p>

          <div class="story-content">
            <div class="story-text slide-in">
              <p>
                What started as a quiet passion for handcrafted wine grew into a
                place where friends, families, and guests gather to celebrate
                and connect. From our earliest small-batch barrels to the
                vibrant winery we are today, Pine Ridge remains focused on
                quality, community, and authentic hospitality. Every bottle
                reflects our dedication to thoughtful craftsmanship, while every
                visit is shaped by a genuine desire to create meaningful
                experiences. Rooted in tradition yet always evolving, Pine Ridge
                Winery invites guests to slow down, savor the moment, and become
                part of a story that continues to unfold with each shared glass.
              </p>
            </div>

